{"tid":2484481,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[iPhone] OneUi 模擬器","createTime":"2021-04-11T15:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T15:49:56.000Z","uid":374134,"like":7,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"596017289c7f2a8799063e03a1fef8d880e19016","tid":2484481,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>為了吸引那些正猶豫是否要從 iPhone 換門到 Galaxy 手機的消費者，Samsung 紐西蘭最近做了一款名為 iTest 的 web app，想藉此讓 iPhone 用戶「嚐嚐另一邊的滋味」。iTest 會模擬 Galaxy 裝置的操作介面，讓你在自己的 iPhone 上體驗訊息、設定、主題、Galaxy Store 等功能。很顯然，Samsung 相信這種幾乎無成本的試機體驗，能讓更多 iPhone 使用者至少考慮一下給 Galaxy/Android 一次機會（尤其在這疫情環境下）。<br />\n<br />\n「我們深知對許多用戶來說，更換作業系統平台是一件讓人頗感畏懼的事情。」Samsung 紐西蘭的代表 John Alexander 這麼說道，「我們開發 iTest 的初衷就是想在不用換機的情況下，讓消費者嘗試一下 Samsung 的產品。」感興趣的朋友可以點開<a href=\"https://www.itest.nz/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itest.nz%2F&d=WFG5iCHEkkmufTvr7zh8K%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=7ca6495b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.itest.nz/</a>  ，體驗並沒有機種和地區的限制喔。</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><span class=\"x-small\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iFaD1WL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFaD1WL.png&h=2d96dac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2NOFvQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NOFvQF.png&h=28763169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWKtEJ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWKtEJ1.png&h=bce9a9cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQMLGYr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQMLGYr.png&h=9ca947af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.itest.nz/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itest.nz%2F&d=WFG5iCHEkkmufTvr7zh8K%2F3Ut%2FTlF5